- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation) is a possible category as the paper deals with the complexity analysis of a symbolic computation technique (dependency pair method). 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the complexity of a computational technique (dependency pair method) used in algorithmic analysis of programs. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper deals with the termination analysis of programs, which is an important aspect of software engineering.
